Package com.github.wuic.nut

This package defines what is a nut in WUIC and how to manage it.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
HeapListener This interface represents a listener which expects to be notified of changes when they occur on a particular heap.
Nut The nut is the fundamental element of WUIC nut.
NutDao This interface abstracts the way you can read and eventually save nuts through a particular protocol.
NutDaoBuilder Abstraction of a builder producing NutDao objects.
NutDaoListener This interface represents a listener which expects to be notified of changes when they occur on a particular nut.
 

Class Summary
AbstractNut Base implementation of the Nut interface.
AbstractNutDao An abstract implementation of a NutDao.
AbstractNutDaoBuilder Abstract implementation of what is a NutDaoBuilder.
NutDaoBuilderFactory Factory for NutDaoBuilder.
NutsHeap This class represents a set of nuts.
 

Enum Summary
NutDao.PathFormat This enumeration specifies formats of path specified to create nuts.

This package defines what is a nut in WUIC and how to manage it.
